---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const effectiveDate = 'April 21, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — Arsovo"
  description="The terms under which Arsovo is provided."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-10">Effective date: {effectiveDate}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-800">
      <p>
        By accessing or using <strong>arsovo.com</strong> (the "Site"), you agree to these Terms of Service.
        If you do not agree, please do not use the Site.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Use of the Site</h2>
      <p>
        You may use the Site for personal, non-commercial purposes. You agree not to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Scrape or harvest content in bulk without permission.</li>
        <li>Attempt to disrupt the Site or circumvent security measures.</li>
        <li>Use the Site for any unlawful purpose.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Content &amp; accuracy</h2>
      <p>
        Arsovo publishes opinions, reviews, and technical content. While we test carefully, software
        changes frequently — specifics in any article may be outdated by the time you read it. Always
        verify with the vendor's own documentation before making critical decisions.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        All content on the Site, including text, graphics, and layouts, is owned by Arsovo or used with
        permission. You may quote short excerpts for commentary or review purposes with attribution and a
        link back. Republishing full articles without written permission is not allowed.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Affiliate disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Some links on this Site are affiliate links. If you click one and make a purchase, we may earn a
        commission at no additional cost to you. Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial
        opinions.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Third-party links &amp; services</h2>
      <p>
        The Site contains links to third-party services we do not control. We are not responsible for the
        content or practices of those services.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        The Site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee that the Site will
        be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of harmful components.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, Arsovo shall not be liable for indirect, incidental,
        special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of your use of the Site.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the Site after an update constitutes
        acceptance of the revised terms.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@arsovo.com">hello@arsovo.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
